# ${blackduck_product_name} user role requirements

Overview:

* The Project Creator overall role is required to create ${blackduck_product_name} projects.
* The Project Code Scanner project role, or the Global Code Scanner overall role, is required to populate the project BOM.
* The Project Manager project role is required to generate reports.

Additional details:

* A user with the Global Code Scanner overall role can generate a report, but cannot delete the report. The Project Manager project role is required to delete the report.
